<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html>
    <head>

    <style type="text/css">
        .main-container { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-direction: column; }
        body { font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Arial", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
        p { font-size: 12px; margin: 8px, 0px; max-width: 350px; text-align: center}
        h2 { margin: 16px 0px 8px 0px; }
    </style>

    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="main-container">
            <h2>Welcome to Karma</h2>
            <p>Here we push towards more positive online communication by incentivising towards good behaviour.</p>
            <p>To get started choose an username and password.</p>

            <form action='login' method='POST'>
                <input type='text' name='username' id='username' placeholder='username'/>
                <input type='password' name='password' id='password' placeholder='password'/>
                <input type='submit' name='submit' value='Log in'/>
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>